      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  Passenger
      This abstract class have almost all the functions that a passenger can do, and it holds all the data of the passenger, including his information, his trips, if he is a subscriber or not, and all the reviews and complains he has submitted
      class  SubscriberPassenger
      This class extends the Passenger class, that's because subscriber passenger is a passenger having some more functions, the class has some overriden functions from and some of its own functions
      class  UnsubscriberPassenger
      This class extends the Passenger class, that's because unsubscriber passenger is a passenger having some more functions, the class has some overriden functions from and some of its own functions
